headline: Jabil Announces Appointment of New Chairman, Directors to the Board
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., January 22, 2026--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL), a global engineering, supply chain, and manufacturing solutions provider, today announced that Steve Raymund has been appointed Chairman of its Board of Directors. Additionally, Thomas T. Edman and Raejeanne Skillern have been appointed to its Board of Directors.

headline: Jabil Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., January 22, 2026--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL) announced that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly dividend of $0.08 per share of common stock to shareholders of record as of February 17, 2026. The dividend is payable on March 3, 2026.

headline: Is Sanmina Stock a Smart Buy Before Q1 Earnings Report?
summary: SANM heads into Jan. 26 earnings after buying ZT Systems' data center business, boosting Cloud and AI scale as estimates stay steady.
